dns-update (1.0.4-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Publish signed macOS and Windows release archives alongside the existing
    signed Linux packages and Linux tarballs.
  * Validate native scheduled execution on macOS launchd and Windows Task
    Scheduler before release publishing.
  * Refresh the cross-platform deployment and packaging documentation for the
    released asset set.

